{"id":251134,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-上海马桥镇失地农民进京上访被拦截（图/","date":"2012-09-11T16:30:53Z","modified":"2012-09-11T16:30:53Z","title":"维权网 | 上海马桥镇失地农民进京上访被拦截（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span>（维权网信息员晨晓报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>日</span><span>，上海市马桥镇的部分失地农民买了去北京的火车票，准备到国土资源部等部门上访。然而，一大早马桥镇政府出动大批人马对准备去北京的农民们拦截，每家门口有三、四人看守，有警察、镇政府人员</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>多人在上海火车站监控，只要马桥的农民们出现就抓捕，数人在火车站被拦截。农民们说：你拦得了今天，拦不了明天，你政府不解决问题，我们誓不罢休！</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>上海闵行区马桥镇政府</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2003</span><span>年开始非法倒卖耕地</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13000</span><span>亩，导致</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13000</span><span>亩耕地荒芜至今</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>年，强迫拆迁农民房屋</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">3000</span><span>多户。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>土地被倒卖，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">30</span><span>年的承包合同被收回，政府到现在没有土地补偿，宅基地、自留地被侵吞，发放的房产证是假证，失去了土地的农民们只有拿</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">900</span><span>元的养老金，按照上海市的最低生活标准要</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1400</span><span>元，天天飞涨的物价难以生活。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>从</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2003</span><span>年底开始，失去土地的马桥农民们跑遍了上海三级政府各部门以及中央各政府部门，向中央、地方政府各部门投过无数次控告信。中央巡视组到上海，失地农民去巡视组反映马桥政府倒卖土地的事实，要求中央派调查组对倒卖土地案进行调查，但至今无下文。向三级法院要求立案，法院不立案。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>至</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2012</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>日</span><span>，失去农民到上海治安总队申请游行</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">63</span><span>次不给受理。然后马桥政府动用公权力、专政工具打压农民，多人被关黑监狱、拘留、殴打，有被判刑，有的人甚至被打残、打死。行凶者逍遥法外，没人追究他们的刑事责任，被打死、打残的人依然也讨不到公道。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>联系：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span>江仙妹：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">02164091995</span></div>\n<div><span>宋继荣：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15801716934</span></div>\n<div><span>何季良：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13764096040</span></div>\n<div><span>曹玉燕：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">15800625843</span></div>\n<div><span>沈佩兰：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">13764885120</span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-tRSOwHxXTh8/UE8-aiZnP9I/AAAAAAAAN8o/Nro-8lF3STU/s1600/%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"224\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-tRSOwHxXTh8/UE8-aiZnP9I/AAAAAAAAN8o/Nro-8lF3STU/s320/%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E4%BA%BA%E5%91%98.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>监控人员</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-6LJaWkxnEss/UE8-chXQIKI/AAAAAAAAN8w/dtIIRLIvdcs/s1600/CIMG1710.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"222\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-6LJaWkxnEss/UE8-chXQIKI/AAAAAAAAN8w/dtIIRLIvdcs/s320/CIMG1710.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-7jCC8sJ6HwM/UE8-fFLnabI/AAAAAAAAN84/DE5c04TYj8w/s1600/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%87%B3%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%9A%84%E7%81%AB%E8%BD%A6%E7%A5%A8.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-7jCC8sJ6HwM/UE8-fFLnabI/AAAAAAAAN84/DE5c04TYj8w/s320/%E4%B8%8A%E6%B5%B7%E8%87%B3%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E7%9A%84%E7%81%AB%E8%BD%A6%E7%A5%A8.jpg\" width=\"247\" /></a></div>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5234401782343008803?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe